 continue to expand our product offerings in the emerging markets company fund name isin currency inception date rating risk profile charlemagne capital iom ltd magna eastern european fd a cap ie eur   high the objective of the fund is to achieve capital growth through investments in a diversified portfolio of emerging european  russian securities the fund is a subfund of the magna umbrella fund plc an ireland domiciled uctis fund charlemagne capital iom ltd magna global emrg mkts fd a cap ie eur   high the investment objective of the fund is to achieve capital growth by investment in a diversified portfolio consisting of global emerging market securities the fund is a subfund of the magna umbrella fund plc an ireland domiciled uctis fund charlemagne capital iom ltd magna turkey fund a cap iebr eur   high the investment objective of the fund is to achieve capital growth by investment in a diversified portfolio consisting of turkish securities the fund is a subfund of magna umbrella fund plc which is an open ended investment company authorised by the financial regulator as a ucits charlemagne capital iom ltd magna latin american fd a cap iebrc eur   high the investment objective of the fund is to achieve capital appreciation through investment in a portfolio consisting primarily of latin american securities charlemagne capital iom ltd magna africa a dis iebtb eur   high the investment objective of the fund is to achieve capital growth by investing in equities and to a limited extent debt securities of companies in emea the fund is a subfund of magna umbrella fund plc which is an open ended investment company authorised by the financial regulator as a ucits charlemagne capital iom ltd magna eastern europe r euro cap iebqld eur  null null the objective of the fund is to achieve capital growth through investments in a diversified portfolio of emerging european  russian securities the fund is a subfund of the magna umbrella fund plc an ireland domiciled uctis fund charle